devdoc.details: The smart name format is composed by "name" (bytes16) and "extension" (bytes4). The smart names have id, which is a keccak256 hash avec the "name" and "extension".

userdoc.notice: This contract represents a register of smart name. Users can register and manage smart names, with traditionnal domain name format ("name"."ext"), and associate a record to this smart name. The record is an ethereum address.
